Author Bio▼▲
Peter Barnes is a Presbyterian pastor who lives in Sydney, Australia. He ministers at Revesby Presbyterian Church and lectures in Church History at the Presbyterian Theological College in Burwood. He is married to Lyn, and they have six children.

